### Email Reminder Worker API Examples
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件或 IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client

@baseUrl = https://your-worker.workers.dev
@token = your-admin-token

### 1. Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. List All Reminders
GET {{baseUrl}}/reminders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Specific Reminder
GET {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Create New Reminder
POST {{baseUrl}}/reminders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "登录 DigitalPlat",
  "description": "请登录 DigitalPlat 网站",
  "url": "https://dash.domain.digitalplat.org/",
  "target_email": "liudingandxiao@gmail.com",
  "interval_days": 180
}

### 5. Create Another Reminder (Example 2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reminders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "续费域名",
  "description": "请检查并续费域名",
  "url": "https://domain-registrar.com",
  "target_email": "admin@example.com",
  "interval_days": 365
}

### 6. Update Reminder (Change interval)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interval_days": 90
}

### 7. Update Reminder (Change multiple fields)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "登录 DigitalPlat (更新)",
  "description": "请及时登录 DigitalPlat 网站，避免账号过期",
  "interval_days": 90
}

### 8. Toggle Reminder (Enable/Disable)
POST {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Manual Check (Trigger reminder processing)
POST {{baseUrl}}/check
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Delete Reminder
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reminders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

